desc: Striking, Streamlined and Focus, Orca Freedive wetsuits are designed to perform smoothly for maximum efficiency. Made from a subtile combination of innovative new technologies, they will be the perfect wetsuit to suit any freediver individual needs.

layout.text: Freediving wetsuits. Designed and tested in collaboration with 18X world record holder, William Trubridge. "Best Suit On The Market." (Deeper Blue)
